node.text:
If you truly want to be great, spend every waking hour helping others to be great first.🔥🤔💯😏

So many people want to be Kings and Queens yet they do not know how to be Servants. And they will fail because they desire power but not responsibility. Even worse, they want power for themselves and not for the good of others. This attitude is not only arrogant but will surely lead to destruction.

node.text:
People see what I do and say it’s a “Get rich quick scheme”.
.
I always say, “you better hope it is!”
.
Let me ask you, do you have time to get rich slow?
.
See, somehow most people have been programmed by society to believe that making a lot of money in a short period of time is bad.
.
It must be shady.
.
It must be a scam.
.
But here’s the thing…
.
What’s the difference between a person making $2,000 a month and someone making $10,000 a month?
.
Odds are, the one making $10K/month is adding value to more people. Helping others solve big problems. And they have valuable skills to do so.
.
And that’s what I have taught thousands of people from over to do.
.
I’ve only given them the “how to” that allows them to get better relationships, quit their jobs, and write their own paychecks.
.
Whether they choose to get rich QUICK or SLOW, is up to them.
.
My question to you is...
.
Do you want to get rich quick or slow? Comment below.
